
LAB 3 :

- Calculator is implemented using Expression grammar supporting major operations as given in assignment.

- To specify the precedence among operators yacc %left and %right construct are used with the one coming in lower order having higher precedence.

- line number is handled by flex and its incremented whenever \n is encountered.

- The type of yyval is defined using %union construct in yaac and %type is used for specifying type of non terminals in grammar.


